name: Inuko Finance
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: Inuko Finance is one of the fastest growing communities in paw nation. Inuko Finance has combined new tricks and strategies .The goal of the Inuko Finance protocol is to create a decentralised, censorship resistant reserve currency for the emerging Web3 ecosystem. Developing a reserve currency is important because the fundamental goal of the Web3 financial movement is to foster an alternative economic ecosystem. Inuko Finance has a static reflection that rewards holders in the form of stable coins, USDT, and  are automatically added to your wallet each transaction.
